flowchart LR
  MATCH[Probabilistic Matching] --> REVIEW[Gray-Zone Human Review]
  VALID[Validated Data] --> MARTS[Governed Marts]
  MARTS --> EXPORTS[Masked CSV / Parquet Exports]
  RAW[Raw Snapshot] --> LINEAGE[Run + Field Lineage]
  MARTS --> LINEAGE
  EXPORTS --> LINEAGE
  ASSETS[Asset Orchestrator] --> RAW
  ASSETS --> VALID
  ASSETS --> MARTS
  ASSETS --> TELEMETRY[Safe Traces + Metrics]
  ID[Demo / OIDC-ready Identity] --> AUTHZ[Organization + Permission Checks]
  AUTHZ --> EXPORTS
  AUTHZ --> REVIEW
  AUTHZ --> AUDIT[Attributable Audit Events]
  RETENTION[Retention Policies] --> EXPORTS
